task.summary: Default task
Using SortedSet instead of sorting when things added
Fixed SortedSet remove() player dupe bug and fixed up Pathfinding
got pathfinding working better and added pathfinding to other entities
Massive commit after git problems. commit includes: pathfinder tweaks, Containers, inventories, Items, new Ai, and entity drops
changed Tile Obstruction to have less knowledge
added missing files
fixed ai problems due to Obstruction being less aware
fixed crashes due to moving rendering to UI thread
started to work on lighting overlay
got basic damage system in place
fixed modifier to be accurate renamed damage resistance to damage modifier because of ability to have weaknesses (trees now strong against blunt weak against fire)
Added Visual representation of being damaged
added heal from damage for things like fire monsters being attacked by fire
fixed pathfinding bug where it couldn't path to recently dropped items
fixed ai bug where npc could still use chest after it died
added attacking
fixed multiple trees in same location errors
fixed pathfinding failure causing deadlock of game
added basic move to and attack entity ai
fixed useChestAi so it fully completes before being interrupted by lower priority tasks
fixed up attack ai to use melee attack
added farm entities for drops ai
added npc attack animation
fixed some pathfinder freezing up problems
Added Skeleton that attacks the player and respawn mechanics
Added Weapon items and an attack cooldown system
added mild randomization to respawn location so monsters can't spawn-camp the player
added spawner areas that will generate entities within a rectangle
Made Collect Items from Entities ai a bit smarter now only kills entities it can gather something from
added weapon render its self so weapon types look different
Added world spawn mechanics and added a lot of more art
Added small house builder
tweaked house generation and added art
Fixed collision so large hitboxes work and pulling is no longer a thing
fix issue with trees being inside of buildings
made doors usable entities and started adding stair tiles
fixed weapon attack area to be correct in 3d space
Added user ability to use usable entities
Started to add Regions
Finished major reorganization to allow Regions
fixed most systems broken by reorganization to allow Regions
Fixed remaining issues with Region addition
added building interiors and player inventory UI
Added chest inventory UI and fixed some issues with player inventory
